item.title: CVE-2017-14384|2024-09-16T22:30:59.956Z -- dell%20emc -- dell%20storage%20manager
item.description: In Dell Storage Manager versions earlier than 16.3.20, the EMConfigMigration service is affected by a directory traversal vulnerability. A remote malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to read unauthorized files by supplying specially crafted strings in input parameters of the application. A malicious user cannot delete or modify any files via this vulnerability.
